aa(lp92
VNow, for thousands of years, we have been studying the cosmos,
p93
aVwe've been wondering about our place in the universe.
p94
aVThe ancient Greeks told us
p95
aVthat the Earth was the center of the universe.
p96
aVFive hundred years ago, Copernicus displaced the Earth,
p97
aVand put the Sun at the heart of the cosmos.
